      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ECHOES OF DAD (1) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at 14 of 31 starts including 13 wins but missed the frame latest when seventh (34.71) over 600m at The Meadows. Hard to go past form here at this journey. Drawn the rails and rates a key runner. TIME TO FIRE (4) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by one length (34.43) at this track. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. SMOOTH DYNAMITE (2) recorded one of the quickest times on the card this course and distance last time, finishing second in a OPEN in 34.50 and a new PB here. Expected to feature again. GINNY'S RUN (7) is always hard to beat when she races at this trip.",
